OL,9,FA watchdog has found that a police
OL,10,Fforce which was repeatedly in contact
OL,11,Fwith the killers of a nine-year-old
OL,12,Fboy who was assaulted, beaten and
OL,13,Fmurdered in the family home in
OL,14,FWorcestershire, did not sufficiently
OL,15,Ftrain officers to identify child abuse.
