OL,3,CWatchdog finds insufficient police
OL,4,Ctraining before 9-year-old boy's murder
OL,6,FAlfie Steele from Droitwich died in
OL,7,FFebruary 2021 after months of
OL,8,F"indescribable" cruelty, in which he
OL,9,Fsuffered 50 injuries all over his
OL,10,Fbody, and his head was held underwater
OL,11,Fin a bath.
OL,13,FHis mother Carla Scott was jailed for
OL,14,F27 years for manslaughter at Coventry
OL,15,FCrown Court in June 2023, and her
OL,16,Fpartner Dirk Howell is serving at
OL,17,Fleast 32 years for his murder.
OL,19,FA mandatory referral was made to the
OL,20,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,21,F(IOPC) after the court case finished.
