OL,6,FThe IOPC added that Alfie's voice was
OL,7,F"never heard by police" because his
OL,8,Fmother answered questions on his
OL,9,Fbehalf.
OL,11,F"Maybe he's being hit and held under
OL,12,Fthe water"
OL,14,FIt found that a different police
OL,15,Fofficer or police community support
OL,16,Fofficer (PCSO) attended on each
OL,17,Foccasion and Alfie was never spoken to
OL,18,Fby any officer on his own.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@WO]
