OL,4,Ctraining before 9-year-old boy's murder
OL,6,FThe IOPC said an officer recorded that
OL,7,Frandom safeguarding visits would be
OL,8,Fbeneficial, but there is no evidence
OL,9,Fthese took place.
OL,11,FThe watchdog said West Mercia Police
OL,12,Fhas implemented its recommendations,
OL,13,Fsuch as using warning markers to
OL,14,Fhighlight that a child is part of a
OL,15,Fchild protection plan, and reviewing
OL,16,Fpolicies around making referrals to
OL,17,Fchildren's services.
OL,19,FThe force has also "trained hundreds
OL,20,Fmore officers" to ensure children have
OL,21,Fa voice, the IOPC said.
