OL,6,FThe watchdog found no indication of
OL,7,Fmisconduct but has recommended that 10
OL,8,Findividuals should take part in
OL,9,F"reflective practice" to review their
OL,10,Finteractions.
OL,12,F"Eight police constables and two PCSOs
OL,13,Fundertake reflective practice"
OL,15,FIOPC director Derrick Campbell said in
OL,16,Fa statement "First and foremost, my
OL,17,Fthoughts and sympathies remain with
OL,18,FAlfie's family and everyone affected
OL,19,Fby his tragic and shocking death.
