OL,6,F"Our investigation has been
OL,7,Fpainstakingly thorough, examining
OL,8,Fhundreds of documents, spanning the
OL,9,Fyears that West Mercia Police had
OL,10,Fcontact with Alfie, his mother and her
OL,11,Fpartner.
OL,13,F"It is important to note that in most
OL,14,Fof the incidents, officers did take
OL,15,Fsome positive action and children's
OL,16,Fservices were appropriately made aware
OL,17,Fof every single police attendance.
OL,19,F"Many other concerns, not shared with
OL,20,Fthe police, were dealt with at local
OL,21,Fauthority level.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
