OL,4,Ctraining before 9-year-old boy's murder
OL,6,F"We found no indication of misconduct
OL,7,Fby any individual officer, but we
OL,8,Frecommended that eight police
OL,9,Fconstables and two PCSOs undertake
OL,10,Freflective practice to review how they
OL,11,Fhandled interactions concerning Alfie.
OL,13,F"In our view, when called to the home,
OL,14,Fofficers should have found a way to
OL,15,Fspeak to Alfie without other adults
OL,16,Fbeing present, in line with best
OL,17,Fpractice.
OL,19,F"On some occasions officers lacked
OL,20,Fprofessional curiosity and could have
OL,21,Fundertaken further inquiries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
