OL,6,F"A culture of fear"
OL,8,F"There was a culture of fear within
OL,9,Fthe household which, when coupled with
OL,10,Flockdown, severely reduced Alfie's
OL,11,Fworld.
OL,13,F"There were few opportunities for
OL,14,FAlfie to feel safe enough to make a
OL,15,Fdisclosure to professionals about what
OL,16,Fwas happening within the family home.
OL,18,F"Carla Scott contributed greatly by
OL,19,Ffailing to safeguard him and failing
OL,20,Fto put his safety and wellbeing before
OL,21,Fher loyalty to her partner.
OL,26,@pD@AOUzD@AOU
