OL,6,F"In that cruel environment, Alfie
OL,7,Fappears to have had to adopt extreme
OL,8,Fcompliance, evidenced by him being in
OL,9,Fbed allegedly asleep on many of the
OL,10,Foccasions the police were called,
OL,11,Fsometimes within a short time of a
OL,12,Freported incident.
OL,14,F"It is reassuring that West Mercia
OL,15,FPolice have committed to ensuring that
OL,16,Feveryone who works in the force knows
OL,17,FAlfie's story.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
