OL,6,FIn a statement, Deputy Chief Constable
OL,7,FRachel Jones from West Mercia Police
OL,8,Fsaid:
OL,10,F"The loss Alfie's family has
OL,11,Fexperienced is immeasurable and we
OL,12,Fcontinue to extend our deepest
OL,13,Fcondolences to those who knew him and
OL,14,Fwill forever miss him.
OL,16,F"Alfie died after he was inflicted
OL,17,Fwith indescribable abuse at the hands
OL,18,Fof his mother and her partner and both
OL,19,Fare now serving considerable prison
OL,20,Fsentences for his death.
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOU
