OL,6,F"The death of a child in such horrific
OL,7,Fcircumstances is abhorrent and in the
OL,8,Fimmediate aftermath of Alfie's death
OL,9,Fwe carried out a review.
OL,11,F"This led to significant changes and
OL,12,Ftraining put in place for our
OL,13,Ffrontline officers and staff to ensure
OL,14,Fthe signs of child abuse and
OL,15,Fvulnerability are fully understood.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
