OL,6,F"To ensure an independent assessment
OL,7,Fand that appropriate scrutiny was
OL,8,Fapplied, in June 2023, we referred our
OL,9,Fcontact with the family prior to
OL,10,FAlfie's death to the Independent
OL,11,FOffice for Police Conduct.
OL,13,F"It is essential we do everything
OL,14,Fwithin our powers to keep children
OL,15,Fsafe, and that our communities have
OL,16,Ffaith that we will do everything to
OL,17,Fkeep children safe.
OL,19,F"There is no doubt protecting children
OL,20,Fis one of the most important things we
OL,21,Fdo.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
