OL,6,F"Since then, we have extended this
OL,7,Ftraining to raise awareness to all
OL,8,Fofficers and staff the importance to
OL,9,Fcapture the voice of the child ` using
OL,10,Fprofessional curiosity to speak and
OL,11,Flisten to children and understand
OL,12,Ftheir fears and concerns. Or what they
OL,13,Fdon't say.
OL,15,F"It has been our mission to share
OL,16,FAlfie's story with our entire
OL,17,Fworkforce to highlight the importance
OL,18,Fof this and how vital it is we get it
OL,19,Fright. We must put safeguards in place
OL,20,Fto make sure no child ever suffers
OL,21,Flike that again.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
